A Wales, 'yan'uwa suna damuwa cewa za su iya zama kamar 'yan kaji
Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi hamayya da shawarar cewa su canza sunan su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament of the UPA).
Wannan taron ya faru ne saboda manufar canza sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
Ƙungiyoyin siyasa na UAE suna damuwa cewa wannan zai haifar da ba'a.
Wani dan kungiyar kwadago ya ce yana damuwa da cewa kungiyarsa "ta yi daidai da Twp da Pwp".
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: a cikin Welsh, twp  yana nufin wawa da pwp - mai lalata.
Ƙungiyar ta Scotland ta ce "ba ta da izini" kuma ta ba da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani dan Wales mai tsaron gida ya ce kungiyarsa tana da "farkon ra'ayi" game da sauya sunan, amma ya lura cewa wannan shine gajeren canji daga MWP zuwa Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, haruffan Welsh w ana furta su kamar haruffan Turanci na Yorkshire u.
Hukumar Majalisar, wadda a halin yanzu ke samar da dokoki don aiwatar da canje-canje a cikin sunan, ta bayyana cewa: "Tabbas, za a yanke shawarar karshe game da kowane bayanin yadda za a kira mambobin Majalisar, wanda mambobin za su yanke shawara kansu".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da ikon canza sunan majalisar dokokin Wales.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta buga sakamakon tattaunawar jama'a game da shawarwari, wanda ya cancanci a kira majalisa a matsayin majalisar dokokin Wales.
Game da sunan A.A., Hukumar ta amince da 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales ko WMP (UPA), amma MWP ya sami babban goyon baya a cikin tattaunawa ta jama'a.
A.A. sun gabatar da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka masu banbanci, amma ana tsammanin zai iya zama ciwon kai ga jami'in da ke gwagwarmaya don cimma yarjejeniya, Elaine Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da manufar doka game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Za a gabatar da wasu canje-canje ga tsarin tsarin majalisar a cikin kundin dokokin game da gyare-gyare, daga cikinsu akwai dokoki masu tsauri na majalisar da kuma tsarin kwamitoci.
A lokacin da ake jayayya game da yadda za a kira doka, A.A. zai iya sa kuri'a ta ƙarshe.
