Ford ya gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Kawano ya yi zaton cewa ya sha kashi 100 cikin ɗari kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinsa a lokacin taron makaranta.
Kavano ya ce a cikin jawabinsa mai ban sha'awa, ya gaskata da cewa ba zai yiwu ba.
A ranar Jumma'a, Nielsen ya ce mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 za su iya kallon wannan bidiyon.
Kamfanin yana lissafin yawan kallon tashar a CBS, da ABC, NBC, da CNN, Fox News da MSNBC.
Ba a san lambobin ba a lokaci guda ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana da wasu matsaloli game da yadda ake auna mutane a ofisoshinsa.
Idan muka yi la'akari da wannan a nan gaba, yawan masu sauraro zai zama kamar na wasan kwallon kafa na wasan kwaikwayo ko kuma na Oscar.
Nielsen ya ce, Fox News, wanda masu watsa shirye-shiryensa suka amince da sanya Kawano, yana kula da dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa tare da masu kallo miliyan 5.69.
ABC ta biyu ne da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 da NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 da CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Bayan sun saurara, sai suka daina son saƙon.
A ranar Jumma'a, Flake ne ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a wasan kwaikwayo.
Bayan da ofishin matsakaicin Republican ya buga takardar neman kuri'a ga Kawan, a safiyar Juma'a an kama shi da kyamarorin CNN da CBS, inda masu zanga-zangar suka yi ihu, yana ƙoƙarin hawa zuwa sauraron kwamitin kotu a cikin lif.
Ya kwanta na 'yan mintoci kaɗan yana kallon ƙasa yayin da CNN ke watsa shirye-shiryensa.
Sai wata mace ta ce, "Ga ni nan a gabanka".
Kana ganin abin da kake faɗa game da ƙasar gaskiya ne?
Kuma suka ce: "Ka kasance mai yawan mãtã, kuma yawancinsu bai kasance mai ƙarfi ba".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ne ya yi wannan bukatar kuma kafin a rufe motar, zai yi karin bayani a taron da aka yi a kwamitin.
Dole ne a yi kuri'a na sa'o'i kadan bayan da aka gabatar da gidan waya da kuma gidan rediyo na kai tsaye don kada kuri'ar da za a gabatar da takarar kwamitin shari'a ga cikakken majalisar dattijai.
Sai dai Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan FBI ta duba tuhumar da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa.
Flake ya tabbatar da tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Democrat, Chris Coons.
Bayan ya yi magana da Kunce da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Zaɓin Flake ya sami ƙarfin kansa, saboda ba za a iya amincewa da Kawano ba sai dai idan an bincika shi a cikin 'yan Republican.
