An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena a Willing, wanda a yau zai iya "haɗa magoya bayan jihar Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya haskaka su daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
