Trump yana ƙoƙarin tallafawa dan takarar Sanata na Jamhuriyar West Virginia Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke gudana a zaben.
"Domin Morrissey, shugaban kasa ya kamata ya yi kokarin kara masa karfin gwiwa a zaben, wanda ba alama ce mai kyau ba", in ji wani mai rahoto na Reuters, Simon Hyder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia.
