HIV / AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta ba da sanarwar cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Sama da mutane 820,000 ne suka ji rauni a kasar, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018, an sami kusan sabbin shari'o'i 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun faru ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji a baya.
A al'adance, cutar ta kamu da cutar ta hanyar zubar da jini da aka yi amfani da shi a wasu sassan kasar Sin.
Amma a wannan hanyar, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar ta HIV ya ragu zuwa sifili, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
A shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a China.
An dakatar da cin zarafin jima'i a kasar Sin a 1997, amma ana nuna bambanci ga LGBT.
Saboda ra'ayoyin da suka dace na kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza suna auren mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya ta jima'i.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a ko'ina.
