Mene ne bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya, kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar za a yi bikin a birnin New York mai suna Global Citizen Festival, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke tattare da manyan taurari da kuma manufar da ke da tasiri: yaki da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai da ta gabata, dubun dubatar mutane za su taru a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don bikin Global Citizens Festival, wanda shine ainihin manufar kawar da talauci ta hanyar 2030 ba don jin daɗin ayyukan kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don sanin abin da ya faru.
Bikin 'Yan ƙasa na Duniya, wanda aka sanar a 2012, ya ba da shawarar fadada aikin talauci na duniya, ƙungiyar kare jama'a ta duniya, ta yi fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar ƙara yawan masu gwagwarmaya da ke fama da shi.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (idan ba ku yarda ku biya VIP-tikiti ba), masu sauraro za su iya yin aikin sa kai, ta hanyar aikawa da imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, ta hanyar kiran waya, ko kuma don sanar da manufar su ta hanyar yaki da talauci.
Amma, a cikin shekaru 12, yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara wajen cim ma burinsa?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ta kyauta hanya ce ta gaske don tabbatar da gayyatar mutane zuwa wani taron, ko wani abu da ake kira "klyctivism" - mutane suna ganin sun yi canji ta hanyar sanya hannu, yin kira ta yanar gizo ko tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya rubuta fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" daga magoya bayansa, yana turawa ga dalilai daban-daban.
Wannan ya nuna cewa, saboda waɗannan ayyukan, shugabannin duniya sun sanar da cewa za su ɗauki manufofin da za su biya dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta sanar da ayyukanta na 390 da aikace-aikacen da suka fito daga aiki, wanda aka biya ko kuma an jawo akalla dala biliyan 10.
A cewar ƙungiyar, asusun da aka ba su sun shafi mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wani babban alhakin da kungiyar The Power of Nutrition ta Birtaniya ta yi shi ne taimaka wa yara su cika makamashi, ta yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda, tare da fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Global Citizens don dakatar da cin abinci a wannan yanki.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayarwa, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, zamu iya kawo ƙarshen rashin adalci na zamantakewar abinci a tarihi", in ji Jakadan abinci Tracy Ullman kai tsaye ga jama'a a wani taro a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Har ila yau, ƙungiyar ta ba da rahoton cewa bayan an ɗauki fiye da 5,000 na'urori a Burtaniya don inganta ciyarwar iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da kuɗin aikin "Food Power", wanda abubuwan da za a yi a ciki za su shafi iyaye mata da yara miliyan 5.
