Sabon manufar samar da mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da majalisar daukaka kara ta Immigration ta yanke a shekarar 2014, wanda ya ba da damar neman mafaka ga baƙi marasa takaddun da ke guje wa tashin hankali a cikin iyali.
Babban mai gabatar da kara na gundumar Columbia, Carl Racine, ya ce a ranar Juma'a: "Sabuwar manufofin ba su da alaka da dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa da dama.
A karkashin dokar tarayya, yanke shawara game da buƙatun neman mafaka dole ne a yanke bisa ga ainihin abubuwan da ke cikin buƙata da yanayin da ake buƙata, kuma irin wannan hanawa ya keta wannan ka'idar, - in ji wani bincike na shawarwari da aka gabatar ga kotu.
