Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da yin ba'a ta hanyar tallan propaganda
Wata mako bayan da jaridar hukuma ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafuka hudu a cikin jaridar Amurka game da amfanin cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada propaganda.
Bayan Amurka ta zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ambaci wani aikace-aikacen biyan kuɗi na China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, mafi sayarwa a jihar Iowa a ranar Laraba da ta gabata - amma China ta musanta zargin.
A cewar wani jami'in Amurka da ya ruwaito Reuters, zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na tsoma baki a zaben Amurka shine sabon mataki na yakin neman zaben Washington na matsa lamba kan China.
Yana da kyau a yi amfani da tallace-tallace na ƙasashen waje don inganta kasuwanci, amma Beijing da Washington ba su iya fita daga tashin hankalin yakin cinikayya a halin yanzu ba, wanda ya bayyana a cikin ƙara yawan farashin da aka yi wa juna.
Masana a kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce, an yi amfani da kudaden da kasar Sin ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don hana masu fitar da kaya daga jihohin da suka fi so kamar Iowa, wanda Trump ya kafa a jam'iyyar Republican.
Jakadan Amurka a China, Terry Brenstead, tsohon gwamnan jihar Iowa, wanda shine babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kuma 'yan kasuwa lahani.
"Shugaban kasar Sin ya kara yawan zargi da kuma zargi ta hanyar yada labaran da ke cikin kafofin watsa labarai na 'yanci", in ji jaridar Brenssted Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da 'yancin magana da kuma kafofin watsa labarai, al'adar da Amurka ta yi, ta ba da tallace-tallace a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register don yadawa, "in ji Brenstead.
Ba kamar Amurka ba, idan aka yi la'akari da cewa jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin tana da iko sosai a kan kafofin watsa labarai, ba za ku sami masu nuna rashin amincewa a nan ba - a cikin tashoshin jaridu a titunan Beijing kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayin jama'ar Sin game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China mai wahala ba," ya rubuta.
Daya daga cikin shahararrun jaridu na kasar Sin ya ƙi buga labarin na, "Ya kara da cewa, ko da yake bai bayyana wane jarida ba.
