A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sami damar canza Intanet ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya yi magana mai kyau a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
