An jinkirta sabon jirgin Jamus na shekara guda
Ana sa ran sabon jirgin ruwan sojojin ruwa na Jamus zai fara aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Cold War, amma har yanzu ba zai isa wurin ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da farashin da ke saurin tashi, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
Jaridar Die Zeit (Zaman) ta ruwaito cewa an jinkirta shigar da sabon jirgin ruwan na Baaden-Württemberg mai suna Rhinland-Pfalz a cikin aiki har zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, tare da danganta ga wakilin soja.
Jirgin ya kamata ya shiga cikin sojojin ruwa a shekara ta 2014, amma matsalolin da suka taso bayan ƙaddamar da shi sun canza makomar wannan aikin mai ban sha'awa.
Kwanan nan, jiragen ruwa hudu na nau'in Baden-Württemberg, wanda sojojin ruwa suka ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007, za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na nau'in Bremen.
Jirgin zai kasance tare da wasu fasahohin stealth kamar ƙirar ƙarfi, ƙirar zeniya da makamai masu linzami, da kuma rage radin, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran muhimman abubuwan da ke cikin wannan fasalin sun fi tsayi: sababbin jiragen ruwa suna bukatar su iya aiki har zuwa shekaru biyu a tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma jaridar Die Zeit ta ce, jiragen ruwa masu ci gaba suna yin sanyin gwiwa domin suna jinkirin shiga cikin jirgin domin su nuna ƙarfin Jamus a ƙasashen waje.
Fregat F125 ya shiga cikin jaridu a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da sojojin Jamus suka ƙi amfani da jirgin kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blem und Foss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da aka mayar da wani jirgin ruwa ga mai ginin da ba a yi amfani da shi a cikin jirgin ruwa.
Ba a san komai game da dawo da jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarun Jamus sun rubuta game da ƙarancin software da kayan aiki a cikin jirgin, wanda ke nufin cewa jirgin ba shi da amfani a aikin soja.
Yana da mahimmanci a cikin shirin cewa jirgin ruwa ba shi da isasshen kayan aiki, saboda a cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg na jirgin ruwa akwai kusan 120 mutane, wanda shine rabin ma'aikata a cikin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Ƙari ga haka, yawan nauyin jirgin yana hana sojojin da ke cikin jirgin ruwa su ƙara sababbin abubuwa.
An yi la'akari da nauyin jirgin Rhineland-Pfalz na 7,000 sau biyu fiye da na irin wannan rukunin jirgin da Jamus suka yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga kayan aikin da ba a gina ba, farashin aikin  har da horar da ma'aikatan  ya zama babbar matsala.
An san cewa farashinsa zai kai na euro biliyan 3,1 idan aka kwatanta da na farko na euro biliyan 2,2 (dolar Amurka biliyan 3.6).
Matsalolin da ke tattare da sababbin jiragen ruwa suna da mahimmanci a kwanan nan, saboda kwanan nan an yada rahotanni cewa Jamus ta rage ƙarfin sojojin ruwa.
Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa na cikin teku suna rage yawan jiragen ruwa.
Kuma a lõkacin da ya yi magana, sai ya ƙara zama mai tsanani, domin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa sun tafi, kuma sababbin jiragen ruwa ba su da amfani.
