Rosenstein ya lura da aikin Robert Mueller, wanda shine mai ba da shawara na musamman wanda ke bincika tarayyar Rasha a cikin zaɓen, sadarwa tsakanin Trump da magoya bayan Rasha, da kuma juriya ga hukuncin adalci na shugaban.
