Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi kisa na musamman ga Syphyllum Saippo, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York inda mutane takwas suka mutu, wanda ba a yi amfani da shi a jihar ba tun 1953 don aikata laifi na tarayya.
A watan Oktoba, Saifullo Saipov mai shekaru 30 ya hau motar mota mai suna Home Depot da aka haya a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan don ya kai hari da makamai a kan hanyar keke.
Masu gabatar da kara da suka sanar da cewa za a yi kisa a gundumar New York ta Kudu za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saiyup ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya ji rauni sosai don ya tabbatar da hukuncin kisa.
Bisa ga bayanan kotu, za a iya yanke hukuncin kisa bisa ga waɗannan abubuwa biyu.
Makonni kadan bayan harin, manyan mambobin kotun tarayya sun gabatar da wata sanarwa mai lamba 22 ga Saifullo Saipov; wanda ya gabatar da zarginsa da kisan kai 8 bisa manufar barazana, da kuma satar da lalata motoci da ake amfani da su a cikin ayyukan aikata laifuka da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suka shirya.
An bayyana harin ne a matsayin "matsayi mai kyau da kuma tunani", wanda aka yi da "matsayi, mummunan da kuma mummunan niyya", a cikin ofishin mai gabatar da kara.
"Saipov, ɗan Habibullah, ya kawo baƙin ciki, baƙin ciki da lahani ga dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anne-Lor Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Hernán Ferruchi, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnucco da kuma abokansa", in ji rahoton.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu yawon bude ido ne daga Jamhuriyar Argentina.
Shekaru goma da suka shige, an yi shari'ar kisa ta ƙarshe a gundumar Kudu ta New York.
An samu mai zargin, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe mutum biyu da suka sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na 2009.
An yi kisa na ƙarshe a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya ta New York a shekara ta 1953, shekaru biyu kafin a soma Yaƙin Tsakiyar, a kan wani ma'aurata da aka yanke hukuncin kisa game da yarjejeniyar ɓoye-ɓoye don amfani da Soviet Union, wato, Julius da Ethel Rosenberg.
An kashe iyalin Rosenberg a kan wutar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar bayanan kotu, Saiyпов, wanda ya haife shi a Uzbekistan, bai yi nadama ba a cikin watanni da kwanaki bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya bayyana cewa bai yi laifi ba kuma yana jin daɗi.
A cewar rahoton, Saiyпов ya yi amfani da wayar sa don yin harin bayan ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIL.
Wani jami'in 'yan sanda ya ce ya kuma nemi a saka tutar IS a ɗakinsa na asibiti.
Saiyup ya ƙaryata kansa game da dukan batutuwa 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke aiki a madadin Saipov, ya ce "sun ji rauni" bayan sun san hukuncin da aka yanke musu.
"Mun yi tunanin cewa samun hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifi da kuma samun 'yancin rai a kurkuku zai kara wa aikin da kuma raunukan duk waɗanda suka halarci aikin", in ji David Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar masu kare Saipov sun nemi kotu ta hana shi hukuncin kisa.
