Nancy Pelosi ta kira Brett Kavana "mai rikici", yana da'awar cewa bai dace da aiki a Kotun Koli ba
Shugaban 'yancin majalisar Nancy Pelosi ya kira dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavano, "mai rikici" kuma ya bayyana cewa ba shi da dacewa don aiki a Kotun Koli.
Pelosi ya yi wannan bayani a wata hira da aka yi a ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune a Austin, Texas.
"Idan wata mace ta yi magana a wannan hanyar, za su ce isterica", in ji Pelosi a ranar Alhamis game da yadda ta amsa ga umarnin Kavano a gaban kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai.
Kawano ya musanta cewa ya yi wa Dr. Christine Blaise Ford fyade sa'ad da su biyun matasa ne.
Kawano ya yi magana sosai a lokacin da ya gabatar da jawabinsa, yana yin ihu a wasu lokatai, yana shiru yayin da yake magana game da iyalinsa da kuma shekarun makarantar sakandare.
