Yadda yakin cinikayya na Amurka da China zai iya amfanar Beijing
Masana sun ce farkon tashin hankalin yaƙin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China ya kasance mai ƙarfi, kuma ko da yake har yanzu ba a kammala yaƙin ba, za a iya samun fa'ida ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekarar, yana ba da gargadi na farko game da haraji kan manyan kayayyakin fitarwa na kasar Sin, ciki har da allon hasken rana, sandar da aluminum.
Babban tashin hankali a wannan makon ya danganta da sabon haraji akan kayayyaki na dala biliyan 200 (150 biliyan fam), wanda a zahiri ya shafi rabin duk kayayyakin da Amurka ke shigowa daga China.
A kowane lokaci, Beijing ta ce kwanan nan ta yi amfani da dala biliyan 60 a cikin haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari a kan kayayyakin Amirka.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin kada ta bar Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu mafi girma ba zai mutu ba da daɗewa ba.
Don tilasta wa Washington ya janye yana nufin mika wuya ga bukatun, amma bauta wa Amurka a fili zai zama abin takaici ga Shugaba Xi Jinping na China.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi nasarar yin taswirar da ta dace, matsin lamba daga Amurka na yakin cinikayya zai iya taimakawa China a cikin dogon lokaci, ta hanyar rage haɗin gwiwar tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Abin da ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura za su gane shi shi ne cewa wani gaggawa siyasa a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin da zai iya ba da damar yin amfani da tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa", in ji Abigail Grace, wani masanin kimiyya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Amurka a Asiya.
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira
Syria ta ce tana son ta mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar da yardar rai kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta shafe fiye da shekaru bakwai tana fama da yaƙi.
A jawabinsa a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje, Walid Al-Mu'alam ya ce yanayin ƙasar zai inganta.
"Yanzu yanayin ya fi karko kuma yana da aminci saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gina yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata.
A halin yanzu, an samar da dukkan yanayi don 'yan gudun hijira da ake tilasta musu su bar rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma hanyoyin da suke rayuwa saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe guda don su iya komawa cikin ƙasarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙi a shekara ta 2011, fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar ƙasar.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Mu'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta taimaka wajen sake gina kasar da ta rushe.
Amma ya ce ba zai sami taimako ko kuma taimako daga ƙasashe da ke tallafa wa 'yan tawayen ba.
Turai ta ci gasar cin kofin Ryder a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe Kofin Ryder ta hanyar lashe gasar ta Amurka a Le Golf National a 2018 a kusa da Paris, ta hanyar 16.5 zuwa 10.5.
Amurka ta lashe gasar cin kofin Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Turai tun 1993.
Kamfanin Thomas Björn na Denmark ya dawo da kambi na Turai bayan da tawagar ta tara maki 14.5 da ake buƙata don cin nasara a kan Amurka.
Tauraruwar Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya ci Francesco Molinari a wasansa, kuma ya jefa kwallonsa a cikin biyu a cikin 16th.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a duk faɗin zagaye, yana ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka fito da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da gasar ta fara a 1979.
Dan Amurka Jordan Spit ya ci Denmark daga cikin kungiyar Turai ta Thorbjørn Olesen a matsayi mafi ƙasƙanci na 5 da 4.
Mafi kyawun ɗan wasa a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya ci Jan Poulter na Ingila 2 da 1, wanda ya buga gasar cin kofin Ryder ta ƙarshe, mai yiwuwa.
Tsohon tsohon soja na Gasar Ryder takwas, Spaniard Sergio Garcia ya zama mafi kyawun Turai a tarihin gasar tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
