Ina farin cikin samun kofin.
"Kin yi magana game da ƙungiyar, kuma ina farin cikin taimakawa", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar da ta samu a Turai.
Ya ba da fitila ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram wanda ya ci Tiger Woods, almara na golf na Amurka, da 2 da 1 a cikin rabon mutum a ranar Lahadi.
"Ina alfahari da lashe Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon wannan saurayi", in ji Ram mai shekara 23.
