Sabuntawa ta hanyar ruwan sama: Ragewa a Pinellas, Manati da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan na Hukumar Kifi da Yan Adam ta Florida ya nuna cewa a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay, an rage yawan ruwan sama na ruwan sama.
A cewar Hukumar Kifi da Yanayin daji, an gano wasu yanayi daban-daban na ci gaba a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County, yana nufin raguwa a cikin taro.
Ruwan ruwan ya yi nisa daga Arewacin Pinellas zuwa Kudu na Li County, a kan kusan mil 130 na rairayin bakin teku.
Ana iya samun waɗannan wuraren kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma sun ragu idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an lura da matsakaitan taro a Pinellas County ko gefenta, daga ƙananan taro zuwa mafi girma a gefen Hillsborough County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa mafi girma a cikin Manati County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa mafi girma a Sarasota County ko teku, daga ƙananan taro zuwa matsakaitan taro a cikin Charlotte County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa mafi girma a cikin Li County ko a waje da ƙananan taro a cikin Colier County.
An yi rahoton cewa akwai tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu rahotanni game da tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin numfashi a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida ba.
